About this item

  • 【12 IN 1 Power Strip with USB】- The 3-side power strip surge protector with 8AC widely outlets and 4 USB charging ports(Total 5V/3.1A) can power up to 12 devices simultaneously. It could charge your cellphone, laptop, tablet, cameras without a variety of converters, save your space and make your desktop organize, perfect suitable for your desktop or nightstand home, office, travel, college dorm room
  • 【2 x USB C Power Strip】- Added extra 2 USB C ports for your devices, the USB C port can charge up to 5V/3A. USB-A ports can charge up to 5V/2.4A Max, all USB Ports Output is 5V/3.1A, 15.5W max which is 30% faster than other usb c charging station. With smart charging technology, it can auto-detects your devices and can reach faster charging efficiency, perfectly fit for your iphone, ipad, tablet etc
  • 【2.2 IN Wide Space】- The desk power strip with 3-side design that makes it easier to make the plugs not covering any outlet, the 8 AC outlets with 2.2 INCH widely spaced in between outlets, larger than standard socket, fit big adapters without blocking each other. The compact design saves more space, suitable for the home, office, and college dorm room
  • 【Wall Mount & Flat Plug】- The low profile flat plug fits easily in tight spaces; and the right angle flat plug design prevents bottom plug blocking; the 6Ft white braided extension cord is made of pure copper, which has better current carrying capacity (15A). The braided power cord is not easy to deform, durable and more safety; the two mounting holes on back allows this power strip to be securely installed in various applications.
  • 【Overload Surge Protection】- The power surge protector with overload protection protects your electrical appliances from lighting, surges or spikes. The minimum energy-absorbing capacity of 900 Joules. Lighted on/off switch with integrated circuit breaker for overload protection of all outlets.(The "Surge Protected” indicator light on to show your devices are protected)

Product Description

Power Strip Surge Protector with USB C

A Desktop Charging Station

8 WIDE AC outlets with 2.2 inches space in between and 4 USB high-speed charging ports. Charge and power everything from major appliances to your phone.

All-round Safety Protection

Overload protection switch, surge protection, thick braided power cable, fire-retardant shell, combine to provide superior safety.

Compatibility

USB Ports: Phones, tablets, Bluetooth, speakers, power banks, watch, Switch and other USB devices.

AC Outlets: Our home electronic devices, such ad our computer, TV, VCD, Rdio, printer etc.

NOTE：

->The USB charging is NOT Fast Charge QC 3.0, It can meet most USB devices charging needs.

->For your safety, ensure that the current power DO NOT exceed the rated power of 1875W, or it may cause damage to the unit and fire hazards.

->The cable and the plug is UL Listed, the the power stip is ETL Listed.

->When we use the power strip, the electric current can produces sound, if you'r device not exceed 1875W/15A, it's safe.

HANYCONY Surge Protector Power Strip with USB C Ports

Want to find a power strip meet your different needs?

HANYCONY with 3-side design power strip with 8 widely outlets and 2 USB A & 2 USB C charging ports allows you to make reasonable use of the socket. It makes up little space on your desk or floor, and makes your desktop organized, suitable for home and office.

Surge protector can protect your devices from lighting, surges or spikes. Overload protection switch will trip off automatically to protect your devices and your home when power overload.

Wall mount design and right angle flat plug with 5ft extension cord can allow you install this power strip on various places, its a great desk or wall usb charging station for phone, tablet, PC, TV and more.

Specification

  • Rated Voltage: 125 V/ 50/ 60 Hz
  • Rated Current: 15A
  • Maximum Power: 1875W
  • Surge Protector Rating: 1080 joules
  • USB Rated Current: Total Max 3A
  • USB A Ports: Max 5V/2.4A
  • USB C Ports: Max 5V/3A
  • Length of Cable: 5Ft/1.5m

3 Side Outlet Extender

3 Side design 8 widely spaced AC outlets can fit for larger adapters without blocking each other. The compact design saves more space, suitable for the home, office, and college dorm room

Wide Spaced Outlets

2.2 inchces widely spced in between outlets, larger than standard socket, fit big adapters without blocking each other.

Wall Mountable Power Strip

Two holes on back allow you install this power strip on different applications.

Upgraded Extension Cord

The power cord is very thick and has better current carrying capacity, and the braided extension cord is not easy to deform, durable and more safety than other power cord.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
5 out of 5 stars
Works well. Pixel 8a "Charging rapidly".
1. It's a nice upgrade from a previous 8-port old-style surge protector that was just lying on the floor. The side ports help direct some of the cords away from the top so they aren't as obtrusive, space-wise.2. The USB outlets work great for charging my Pixel 8a via direct USB-C (I get "Charging rapidly") and my TOZO T6 Bluetooth earbuds case via direct USB-A to Micro USB.It wouldn't charge my MacBook Air 2022, but that's to be expected as it requires 30W to charge, not 5W. My 30W Apple charger fits nicely in the top outlet though with plenty of room between it and the wall.3. It's light enough to mount on the wall with velcro strips. I used "BRAVESHINE Heavy-Weight Hook and Loop Strips with Adhesive" bought from Amazon. I cut one of those in half and placed them horizontally at the top and bottom to mount it.Edit: The adhesive failed as I was writing the review an hour after placing it there so I will need to find another way to secure it. It does have mounting holes on the back/bottom where you can hang it on screws or nails or something like that which I will probably try next.
